<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٧٠٥٧ -<span class="c5"> حدثنا ابن علية عن ابن جريج قال:</span> أخبرني عكرمة عن مجاهد أنه قال في: ﴿وَأُمَّهَاتُ نِسَائِكُمْ <span class="c2">(وَرَبَائِبُكُمُ)</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span> اللَّاتِي فِي <span class="c2">(حُجُورِكُمْ)</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span>﴾ أريد <span class="c2">(بهما)</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢٤٥⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(الدخول)</span> <span class="c2">(٤)</span> <span class="c2">(جميعًا)</span> <span class="c2">(٥)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
